{"id": "test-00793", "text": "Spain coach Javier Clemente has added uncapped Deportivo Coruna midfielder Armando Alvarez to his squad for the World Cup qualifier against Yugoslavia on December 14.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 5, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Spain"}, {"start": 12, "end": 27, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Javier Clemente"}, {"start": 47, "end": 63, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Deportivo Coruna"}, {"start": 75, "end": 90, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Armando Alvarez"}, {"start": 112, "end": 121, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "World Cup"}, {"start": 140, "end": 150, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Yugoslavia"}]}
{"id": "test-00794", "text": "\"I don't believe it ...", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-00795", "text": "I thought it was a joke, \"said Armando who replaces injured Atletico Madrid playmaker Jose Luis Caminero.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 31, "end": 38, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Armando"}, {"start": 60, "end": 75, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Atletico Madrid"}, {"start": 86, "end": 104, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Jose Luis Caminero"}]}
{"id": "test-00796", "text": "SOCCER - FIFA BOSS HAVELANGE STANDS BY WEAH.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 9, "end": 13, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "FIFA"}, {"start": 19, "end": 28, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "HAVELANGE"}, {"start": 39, "end": 43, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "WEAH"}]}
{"id": "test-00797", "text": "ROME 1996-12-06", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 4, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "ROME"}]}
{"id": "test-00798", "text": "FIFA chairman Joao Havelange said on Friday he would personally present AC Milan George Weah with world soccer's fair play award despite the striker's attack on Porto captain Jorge Costa.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 4, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "FIFA"}, {"start": 14, "end": 28, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Joao Havelange"}, {"start": 72, "end": 80, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "AC Milan"}, {"start": 81, "end": 92, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "George Weah"}, {"start": 161, "end": 166, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Porto"}, {"start": 175, "end": 186, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Jorge Costa"}]}
{"id": "test-00799", "text": "In an interview with the Italian newspaper Gazzetta dello Sport, he was quoted as saying Weah had been provoked into the assault which left Costa with a broken nose.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 25, "end": 32, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "Italian"}, {"start": 43, "end": 63, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Gazzetta dello Sport"}, {"start": 89, "end": 93, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Weah"}, {"start": 140, "end": 145, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Costa"}]}
